# Landing Page

This is a simple and responsive landing page created using **HTML** and **CSS**. The design is clean and minimal, aimed at showcasing information effectively.

## Features

- **Responsive Design**: Adjusts seamlessly to various screen sizes.
- **Modern Layout**: A visually appealing design using modern HTML and CSS techniques.
- **Cross-Browser Compatibility**: Works well on all modern browsers.

